<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Nueva Reserva - Sistema de Salones</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #03912e, #02b844);
      color: white;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .header p {
      margin: 10px 0 0 0;
      opacity: 0.9;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px;
    }
    .reserva-info {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 25px;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      border-left: 4px solid #03912e;
    }
    .info-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .info-item {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .info-label {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
    }
    .info-value {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #333;
      padding-left: 22px; /* Para alinear con los √≠conos */
    }
    .creador-info {
      background: #e8f5e8;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 15px;
      text-align: center;
      border: 1px solid #03912e;
    }
    .creador-label {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #03912e;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #03912e;
      color: white;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-left: 8px;
    }
    .footer {
      background: #f1f3f4;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .logo {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #03912e;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .icon {
      font-size: 16px;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }
    .status-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #03912e;
      color: white;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 25px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .turno-detalle {
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #03912e;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>üéâ Nueva Reserva Confirmada</h1>
      <p>Su reserva ha sido creada exitosamente en nuestro sistema</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <div class="reserva-info">
        <div class="info-grid">
          <div class="info-item">
            <span class="info-label">üìÖ Fecha de Reserva</span>
            <span class="info-value">{{fecha_reserva}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-item">
            <span class="info-label">üè¢ Sal√≥n Reservado</span>
            <span class="info-value">{{salon}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-item">
            <span class="info-label">‚è∞ Turno</span>
            <span class="info-value">
              <span class="turno-detalle">{{turno}}</span>
            </span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-item">
            <span class="info-label">üÜî Estado</span>
            <span class="info-value">Confirmada ‚úÖ</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="creador-info">
          <div class="creador-label">üë§ Reserva creada por:</div>
          <div style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin: 8px 0;">{{creado_por}}</div>
          <span class="badge">{{tipo_usuario}}</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="text-align: center; margin: 25px 0;">
        <div class="status-badge">
          ‚úÖ Reserva Confirmada y Procesada
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; text-align: center;">
        <strong>üí° Importante:</strong> 
        <span style="color: #856404;">
